Title: Konchem Ishtam Konchem Kashtam
Actors: Siddharth, Tamannaah Bhatia, Prakash Raj, Ramya Krishnan
Plot: Siddhu always wears a smile on his face but he has sad past. Geeta joins his college. Both fall in love and are ready to get married. But Geeta's father refuses their love unless Siddhu tackle his Past problem.
